folder: Van Cortlandt Avenue & Bainbridge Avenue, Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: Van Cortlandt Avenue - Bainbridge Avenue
text:
Van Cortlandt Ave.,East at the N.W. corner of Bainbridge Ave., showing the Isaac Varian House. The main building was built in 1776.
1899.
Randall Comfort.
